{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/extras/CrabLunge.gif?t=1732736641\" /><br>Play as a happy little parasite living the modern corporate dream: Trying to survive another day in the office. Swing and chomp your way through the vast headquarters of The Coffee Corp, a corporate monument to biological sciences gone awry.<br><br>The Coffee Corp made you, but your instinct set you free.<br><br>Wreak havoc through offices, labs, warehouses and forgotten catacombs and processing units in a physics-based reverse horror experience. Discover new biological abilities, and uncover the depravity of your creators as you make your way deeper in to the facility - driven by instinct and a thirst for fresh blood.<br><br><u><strong>EXPLORE</strong></u><br>Evade capture and explore a hostile world filled with unsuspecting victims and dark secrets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/extras/CrabRun.gif?t=1732736641\" /><br><br><u><strong>EVADE</strong></u><br>Swing over obstacles and avoid traps set by the corporation's security forces.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/extras/CrabSwing.gif?t=1732736641\" /><br><br><u><strong>ENGULF</strong></u><br>Feed on the terrified employees to gain strength and evolve.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/extras/CrabChomp.gif?t=1732736641\" /><br><br><strong><u>GET EVEN</u></strong><br>Use a host of biological abilities to take vengeance on the Coffee Corp and bring their sinister operations to a halt.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/extras/CrabDestroy.gif?t=1732736641\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851800/page_bg_generated_v6b